			<h4><a id="comment_link_64175235" name="comment_link_64175235" href="//hardware.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23199423&amp;cid=64175235" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64175235)" >Re:The range problem is easily solved.</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64175235" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64175235); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>4</a>, Insightful)</span></h4>
